<page>
      <topic>{dialog.object}.activateControlContainer Method</topic>
      <syntax>{dialog.Object}.activateControlContainer()</syntax>
      <description>
            <![CDATA[If a control is inside a Tab or Accordion container, activates the pane in which the control in contained. This method will also activate the PanelCard in which the control has been placed. ]]>
      </description>
      <example>
            <![CDATA[{dialog.Object}.activateControlContainer(Quantity); ]]>
      </example>
      <limitations>Only applies to input controls.</limitations>
      <see>
            <ref href="/documentation/index?search=Dialog Component">{dialog.Object}</ref>
      </see>
      <terms>ux component</terms>
      
      
</page>